[
  {"id":"prisoner_merchant","type":"npc","name":"囚徒商人","biome":"forgotten_prison","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"broken_cell","repeatable":true,"narrative":"一个瘦弱的身影从牢房角落站起来。‘我在等一个人——也许是你。’","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"‘你……是来杀我的吗？’","choices":[{"text":"‘不。我能帮你什么？’","next":"shop","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘是的。’","next":"end","effect":"none","risk":"spawn:elite_orc:1"}]},{"id":"shop","text":"‘谢谢你。我在废墟里找到了一些东西——但我不需要钱。’","type":"trade","trade_items":["equipment:rare","equipment:rare","potion:heal"],"trade_cost":"hp:20","choices":[{"text":"‘成交。’ (以20%HP交换)","effect":"trade","next":"farewell"},{"text":"‘太贵了。’","next":"farewell","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"farewell","text":"‘愿黑暗对你仁慈。’","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[结束]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"old_prisoner","type":"npc","name":"老囚徒","biome":"forgotten_prison","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"","repeatable":true,"narrative":"墙角蜷缩着一个白发老人。他没有抬头。","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"‘又一个迷路的灵魂。坐——如果你不介意这地上的灰。’","choices":[{"text":"‘你是怎么活下来的？’","next":"story","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘我得走了。’","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"story","text":"‘三十年了。他们以为我会疯掉——但他们忘了，我本来就已经疯了。’","choices":[{"text":"‘有什么我能做的吗？’","next":"advice","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘……’","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"advice","text":"‘前面是狱卒的地盘。他不是人——记住，躲开他的剑锋。向左，永远向左。’","choices":[{"text":"[认真点头]","next":"end","effect":"buff:defense_up:1"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"forge_master","type":"npc","name":"熔炉大师","biome":"ash_volcano","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"forge_ruins","repeatable":true,"narrative":"一个浑身伤疤的铁匠站在熔炉旁，抬头朝你点了点头。","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"‘这熔炉炼了一千年——除了我，你是第一个走进来的。’","choices":[{"text":"‘能帮我打造装备吗？’","next":"forge","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘你是谁？’","next":"story","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"forge","text":"‘行。但这火不是免费的——它向你索取。’","type":"trade","trade_items":["equipment:epic"],"trade_cost":"hp:30","choices":[{"text":"‘拿去。’ (以30%HP交换史诗装备)","effect":"trade","next":"farewell"},{"text":"‘算了，太危险了。’","next":"farewell","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"story","text":"‘我叫铁砧。曾是王城最好的铁匠。后来国王的剑断了——你懂的。’","choices":[{"text":"‘你想离开这里吗？’","next":"forge","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘我得走了。’","next":"farewell","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"farewell","text":"‘去吧。下次来的时候，带些好矿石。’","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[结束]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"lost_miner","type":"npc","name":"迷失矿工","biome":"ash_volcano","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"","repeatable":false,"narrative":"一个满脸煤灰的矮人靠在岩壁上，腿被碎石压住了。","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"‘别……别走！我被困住了。帮帮我——我会报答你的！’","choices":[{"text":"搬开碎石 (消耗15%HP)","effect":"none","risk":"hp_loss:15","next":"saved"},{"text":"‘我没有时间。’","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"saved","text":"‘谢谢你！我的圣物——拿去吧，我反正也出不去了。’","choices":[{"text":"[接受]","next":"end","effect":"relic:1"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"watcher","type":"npc","name":"守望者","biome":"void_abyss","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"floating_altar","repeatable":true,"narrative":"一个戴着面具的人站在祭坛中央。他没有呼吸——你也听不到心跳。","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"‘你来了。’","choices":[{"text":"‘你是谁？’","next":"identity","effect":"none"},{"text":"[战斗姿态]","next":"fight","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"identity","text":"‘我是最后一批朝圣者。我们的神死了。我留下来看守他的遗物。’","choices":[{"text":"‘深渊里有什么？’","next":"lore","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘我不需要回答。’","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"fight","text":"‘很好。试吧——你已经杀了很多。不差我一个。’","choices":[{"text":"‘……不。你说得对。’","next":"identity","effect":"none"},{"text":"‘让开。’","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"lore","text":"‘一个名字。一口井。黑暗中养大的东西。你不会想知道的——但你很快就会见到。’","choices":[{"text":"[接受祝福]","next":"end","effect":"buff:blessing:1"},{"text":"[后退一步]","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"void_trader","type":"npc","name":"虚空商人","biome":"void_abyss","trigger":"floor_enter","room":"","repeatable":true,"narrative":"裂缝中走出了一个穿着斗篷的人——脚下没有影子。","dialogue":[{"id":"greet","text":"’我接受任何货币。黄金、记忆、影子——都可以折价。’","choices":[{"text":"’给我看看你的货。’","next":"trade","effect":"none"},{"text":"[转身离开]","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"trade","text":"’这些来自凡人不敢去的地方——你准备好了吗？’","type":"trade","trade_items":["relic:1","equipment:legendary"],"trade_cost":"hp:40","choices":[{"text":"’成交。’ (以40%HP交换1圣物+传说装备)","effect":"trade","next":"farewell"},{"text":"’太贵了。’","next":"farewell","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"farewell","text":"’当你的影子不见了——你知道在哪里找我。’","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[结束]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"hidden_prison_vault","type":"event","name":"隐藏监牢密室","biome":"forgotten_prison","trigger":"wall_interact","room":"","repeatable":false,"conditions":[],"narrative":"你摸索着墙壁——一块石砖微微松动。推开之后，露出一间被遗忘的密室。","dialogue":[{"id":"discover","text":"密室里堆满了守卫没收的囚徒物品——几十年没人碰过了。","choices":[{"text":"搜刮密室","effect":"equipment:epic","next":"end","risk":"spawn:skeleton_archer:2"},{"text":"小心关上暗门","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"volcanic_geode","type":"event","name":"火山晶洞","biome":"ash_volcano","trigger":"wall_interact","room":"","repeatable":false,"conditions":[],"narrative":"你敲击岩壁——一声空洞的回响。几锤下去，岩壳碎裂，露出一座水晶洞穴。","dialogue":[{"id":"discover","text":"洞壁上嵌满了火红的晶石——它们在黑暗中散发着灼热的光芒。","choices":[{"text":"采集晶石 (消耗15%HP)","effect":"relic:2","next":"end","risk":"hp_loss:15"},{"text":"太危险了，离开","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]},
  {"id":"void_memory","type":"event","name":"虚空记忆","biome":"void_abyss","trigger":"wall_interact","room":"","repeatable":false,"conditions":[],"narrative":"虚空裂缝旁的石壁突然变得透明——你看到了一场远古的献祭。一个声音在你脑中响起。","dialogue":[{"id":"discover","text":"’凡人。你触碰到了不该触碰的东西。但我欣赏你的勇气。’","choices":[{"text":"接受虚空的馈赠","effect":"skill_level:2","next":"end","risk":"debuff:curse:1"},{"text":"后退——这不是给你的","next":"end","effect":"none"}]},{"id":"end","text":"","choices":[{"text":"[离开]","effect":"none"}]}]}
